Package eu.mihosoft.freerouting.board

Class Via

java.lang.Object
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.board.Item
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.board.DrillItem
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.board.Via
All Implemented Interfaces:
Connectable, ObjectInfoPanel.Printable, SearchTreeObject, Drawable, ShapeTree.Storable, UndoableObjects.Storable, Serializable, Comparable<Object>
public class Via extends DrillItem implements Serializable
Class describing the functionality of an electrical Item on the board, which may have a shape on several layer, whose geometry is described by a padstack.
